responseText: I can't read this script. It's an old, old Vaelune dialect. The handwriting is beautiful, though. It's a tragedy that we don't know someone who could translate it. I'm sure there's a story here. Nonetheless, if you give it to me, I will be sure to enshrine it in my museum - when I build it.
